## Architecture

This project uses **Vue 3 + Vite 6** with file-based routing:

- **src/pages/** — Page components (lazy-loaded by route)
- **src/stores/** — Pinia state management
- **src/router/index.ts** — Vue Router configuration
- **tests/** — Vitest + @vue/test-utils

Key conventions:

- Routes are defined in `src/router/`, pages in `src/pages/`
- State is managed via Pinia stores (one file per domain)
- Components use `<script setup lang="ts">` composition API
- Composables go in `src/composables/` for reusable logic
- Auto-imports are not used — everything is explicit
